Also, when I double click on like a scar script, it wont open, so i have to right click, and press open with and then scar, and its really annoyng, but now since I cant play runescape, I am realy pissed off, is ther anyway to fix the computer without going o like geeksqaud and paying like 3000000$ to fix the computer? Thanks.
PS Sorry bout grammer, im just typing so fast cause im in a hurry to get it fixed, because parents are blaming me :O
